<html lang="en">

<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main id="eligibility-requirements">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="eligibility-intro">
            <p>Before you donate blood, it's important to make sure you meet the necessary requirements. Here are some
                general eligibility guidelines you should consider.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Eligibility Criteria -->
        <section class="eligibility-section">
            <div class="eligibility-content">
                <img src="./images/eligibility.jpg" alt="Eligibility Criteria" class="eligibility-image">
        
                <div class="eligibility-info">
                    <h2>General Eligibility Requirements</h2>
                    <p>To ensure the safety of both donors and recipients, donors must meet certain criteria. Here are the general eligibility requirements you need to know before donating blood:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Age: Must be at least 18 years old (16-17 with parental consent).</li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Weight: Minimum weight of 50 kg (110 lbs).</li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Health: Must be in good general health and feeling well.</li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Medical History: No recent history of certain diseases or medical conditions.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        
        
        
        

        <!-- Specific Eligibility Information -->
        <section class="eligibility-section">
            <div class="eligibility-content">
                <img src="./images/world-no-tobacco-day-concept.jpg" alt="Health and Medical History"
                    class="eligibility-image">
                <div class="eligibility-info">
                    <h2>Health and Medical History</h2>
                    <p>Blood donation is a simple, safe process, but not everyone is eligible to donate. Some conditions
                        may temporarily or permanently prevent you from donating blood. Here are some specific
                        considerations:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Travel: Recent travel to certain countries may affect
                            eligibility.</li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Medications: Certain medications may prevent you from donating.
                        </li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Tattoos and Piercings: You may need to wait a period after
                            getting a tattoo or piercing.</li>
                        <li><i class="icon-check"></i> Pregnancy: Women who are pregnant or recently pregnant may not be
                            eligible.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>


</body>

</html>